  "id": "019d286a-f2d8-78b2-92cd-422ad26ed8fb",
  "content": "### D74: Declaration + Usage Tracking in Chunking Pipeline\n### D75: Lazy Search-Time Edge Discovery (deferred to M4.1)\n\n## Testing Strategy\n\n**Fix 1 tests (adapter crate):**\n- `RustModuleMap` correctly parses a mini workspace with `Cargo.toml` + `mod` declarations\n- `resolve_rust_module_path()` with module map resolves `crate::config` → `src/config.rs`\n- `super::` resolution works relative to current file\n- Full `chunk_file_with_relations()` produces cross-file import relations\n\n**Fix 2 tests (kernel crate):**\n- Markdown with `` `QueryableStore` `` produces a `\"references\"` relation with `to_name: \"QueryableStore\"`\n- Markdown with `[traits](src/traits.rs)` produces a `\"references\"` relation with `to_file`\n- Common words in backticks are filtered out\n- Short spans and Rust primitives are skipped\n\n**Fix 3 tests (kernel crate):**\n- Two chunks from different files, both mentioning `QueryableStore`, produce a `\"uses\"` relation\n- Same-file references are skipped\n- Standard library types don't produce edges\n- Symbols in 10+ files are skipped\n\n**End-to-end validation:**\n- Re-run benchmark script after all fixes\n- Compare edge count: expect 236 → 500+ edges\n- Compare benchmark results: graph expansion should show meaningfully different source file lists\n\n---\n\n\n## Expected Impact\n\n| Metric | Before | After (estimated) |\n|--------|--------|-------------------|\n| Total edges | 236 | 500-800 |\n| Cross-file edges | ~5 | 300-600 |\n| Graph expansion results/query | 0-2 | 5-15 |\n| Unique relation types | 3 | 5 (`imports`, `implements`, `contains`, `references`, `uses`) |\n| Markdown chunks with edges | 0 | 100-200 |",
  "source_version": "docs/rfcs/2026-03-04-m3.4-graph-edge-improvements-design.md",
